data.description: Location! Location! Location!  Much sought after ranch home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage in Brookhaven!    Home has a feeling of being light, bright & airy!  Features: Oak wood cabinets in kitchen w/stainless steel gas range, dishwasher & microwave, beautiful hardwood flooring in living areas, large dining area, w/ beautiful stone gas fireplace in family room, large master bedroom, master bath has dual sinks, separate tub & shower, wonderful covered patio overlooking large corner lot!  Great driveway and 2-car garage!  This home has been extremely well maintained and is move in ready!  Enjoy the amazing amenities including a lap pool, 3 tennis courts, basketball court and a clubhouse. Conveniently located near shopping and restaurants, making grocery shopping  and running errands a breeze.
